original_title: BREAKING: Kash Patel just CONFIRMED there was NO PREDICATE to raid President Trump’s Mar-a-Lago home  — The Donald
article_summary: Kash Patel confirmed there was no predicate for the raid on President Trump's Mar-a-Lago home, with some commentators calling for the arrest of those involved in creating fake evidence. Critics are frustrated with the lack of criminal prosecutions for various alleged crimes.</s>
